information related to treatment mediators and moderators that was not 
previously possible. Stakeholders interested in tobacco cessation, including 
researchers, clinicians and public health officials, should be aware of this 
initiative and the evidence-base it will generate to advance tobacco treatment 
among this high-risk population.

