Atrial Fibrillation in Indigenous Australians: A Multisite Screening Study Using 
a Single-Lead ECG Device in Aboriginal Primary Health Settings.

Gwynn J(1), Gwynne K(2), Rodrigues R(3), Thompson S(4), Bolton G(5), 
Dimitropoulos Y(3), Dulvari N(6), Finlayson H(5), Hamilton S(4), Lawrence M(7), 
